org.eclipse.scada.configuration.world.deployment

Interface NodeMappings

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    NodeMappingsImpl

    public interface NodeMappings
    A representation of the model object 'Node Mappings'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Entries
    • Fallback Mode

    See Also:
    DeploymentPackage.getNodeMappings()
